OL,5, Coldplay will stop recording music as a
OL,6, band in 2025, frontman Chris Martin has
OL,7, revealed.                              
OL,9,FMartin made the announcement on Radio 2
OL,10,Fon Wednesday, in a clip trailing ahead 
OL,11,Fto his Christmas Show with Jo Whiley on
OL,12,Fthe same channel on Thursday evening.  
OL,14,F"Our last proper record will come out  
OL,15,Fin 2025, and after that I think we will
OL,16,Fonly tour," he said.                   
OL,18,F"And maybe we'll do some collaborative 
OL,19,Fthings but the Coldplay catalogue, as  
OL,20,Fit were, finishes then."               
